      "date": "2016-11-16 22:19:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nDoes this disable GSS and Kerberos completely for SLES11?\n\nIt looks that way, but this would break Kerberos completely for SLES11.  Instead, I've cobbled together a patch to disable only the SSK functionality if this doesn't work.\n\nNot able to test locally, but have pushed it as http://review.whamcloud.com/22806 to try on the build farm.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "5f04b221201e782a6da2553c0d3a58b6517f6ac5",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2016-11-16 22:19:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI've fixed http://review.whamcloud.com/22806 to disable only the SSK build for SLES11 instead of all GSS, so I think this patch should be abandoned and the later patches rebased on top of that one.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
