        "subject": "LU-3289 gss: Add autoconf check to prevent GSS with SLES11",
        "message": "LU-3289 gss: Add autoconf check to prevent GSS with SLES11\n\nSLES11 does not have the library functions to support shared key\nso disable GSS when the proper functions are missing or incorrect\nwith that OpenSSL version.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeremy Filizetti <jeremy.filizetti@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: I9492193e84f7be4e7fbf8f7278a6f37a7531c997\n"
      },
